OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,FIn his first sit-down interview since
OL,7,Flaunching his bid to return to
OL,8,FWestminster, Andy Burnham has said
OL,9,Fbecoming an MP would be the "first
OL,10,Fstage" in his fight to change Labour
OL,11,Fand the country.
OL,13,FBurnham is widely expected to launch a
OL,14,Fleadership challenge against Keir
OL,15,FStarmer, if he wins the by-election in
OL,16,FMakerfield later this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,FAsked if he wanted to be the leader of
OL,7,Fthe Labour Party, Burnham said: "I
OL,8,Fwill take that fight as high as I can
OL,9,Ftake that fight, because I think the
OL,10,Fcountry does need to change," he told
OL,11,FITV News' Daniel Hewitt.
OL,13,F"I've indicated that always in my role
OL,14,Fas Mayor, that one day I will seek to
OL,15,Freturn to Westminster. So I'm saying
OL,16,Fthat now and I don't know whether
OL,17,Fpeople here feel that that's something
OL,18,Fthey want to support, but that is the
OL,19,Ffirst stage and I'm not getting ahead
OL,20,Fof myself."
OL,26,@uD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,F"It's for others to decide as well
OL,7,Fwhether I'm the person to lead that
OL,8,Ffight forward. I want this by election
OL,9,Fto be a change moment for British
OL,10,Fpolitics."
OL,12,FBurnham spoke on Saturday with ITV
OL,13,FNews in Makerfield, a constituency on
OL,14,Fthe border of Greater Manchester and
OL,15,FMerseyside.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
