PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,FIt is the Mayor of Greater
OL,7,FManchester's first interview since he
OL,8,Fwas cleared to run as a candidate in
OL,9,Fthe by-election by the Labour Party's
OL,10,Fruling body the NEC ` after the
OL,11,Fcurrent MP Josh Simmons quit to make
OL,12,Fway for him to stand.
OL,14,FAsked why, when he has spent the past
OL,15,Fdecade being critical of Westminster,
OL,16,Fhe wants to come back, Burnham said he
OL,17,Fthinks country is broken.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,F"Everyone can feel that the country's
OL,7,Fnot working, it's not where it should
OL,8,Fbe and politics isn't working. It
OL,9,Fworks for some people in some places,
OL,10,Fbut not all people in all places."
OL,12,FIf he wins the by-election and becomes
OL,13,Fan MP, Burham is widely expected to
OL,14,Fmount a leadership challenge against
OL,15,FSir Keir Starmer. It is expected the
OL,16,Fby-election date will be set on June
OL,17,F18, with some reports suggesting
OL,18,FBurnham is looking to become leader by
OL,19,Fsummer.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,FAmid widespread rumours he is
OL,7,Fultimately set to launch a bid for
OL,8,FNumber 10, Burnham refused to answer
OL,9,Fwhether he had confidence in Keir
OL,10,FStarmer as Prime Minister.
OL,12,F"I've always worked with (Starmer) and
OL,13,FI do have, you know, confidence in him
OL,14,Fas a person," he said.
OL,16,FIn a bid to distance himself from the
OL,17,Fcurrent government, Burnham also
OL,18,Frefused to say whether he wants
OL,19,FStarmer to join him on the doorstep,
OL,20,Finsisting he is running a "different
OL,21,Fcampaign" to the Prime Minister.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@ZpmtD@bpnvD@MO]|D@[OU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,F"I'm saying different things to a
OL,7,Fdegree, in terms of what the
OL,8,Fgovernment has been saying.
OL,10,F"If people want to come and join the
OL,11,Fcampaign, then, you know, (they can)
OL,12,Fbut I'm not saying everybody must come
OL,13,Fand join (...) because it is a
OL,14,Fdifferent campaign."
OL,16,F"I'm standing on a call for change
OL,17,Faren't I? I think we need to change
OL,18,FLabour to some degree so we can change
OL,19,Fpolitics, change the country."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUsD@[pmsD@dpnuD@JpmuD@NpnvD@
OL,26,ATO]xD@AOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
