PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,FDespite the fact he is not yet an MP,
OL,7,FBurnham is widely seen as the
OL,8,Ffavourite in a race that could include
OL,9,Fthe former Health Secretary Wes
OL,10,FStreeting and former Deputy Prime
OL,11,FMinister Angela Rayner.
OL,13,FBurnham praised Rayner, who he called
OL,14,Fhis "close friend" - and the other
OL,15,Fpotential front-runners Streeting and
OL,16,Fcurrent Energy Secretary and former
OL,17,FLabour Leader Ed Miliband.
OL,19,F"All through my career I've supported
OL,20,FAngela. I'm close friends with
OL,21,FAngela," he told ITV News.
OL,26,@vD@EOUvD@RO]{D@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,F"Wes Streeting is an incredibly
OL,7,Fcapable politician, as is Keir, as is
OL,8,FEd Miliband. And as you know, there's
OL,9,Fso many."
OL,11,FBut he will first have to win in
OL,12,FMakerfield ` which is not an easy
OL,13,Fchallenge. The parliamentary seat is
OL,14,Fcurrently held by Labour but Reform UK
OL,15,Fcame second in the 2024 General
OL,16,FElection, and have recently been
OL,17,Fgaining support.
OL,19,FIn nearby Wigan, Reform took 24 out of
OL,20,F25 seats up for grabs in the local
OL,21,Felections last Thursday.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,FDespite their political differences,
OL,7,FBurnham said Farage had always been
OL,8,F"perfectly friendly".
OL,10,F"I've only met him a couple of times.
OL,11,FI. He was perfectly, you know,
OL,12,Ffriendly".
OL,14,F"I get on with people, I try and work
OL,15,Fwith people, but obviously I don't
OL,16,Fagree with his political views."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@TO]rD@AOUtD@IO]vD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,FBurnham was upfront about the
OL,7,Fchallenge Farage's party poses to
OL,8,FLabour. Asked if he understood why
OL,9,Fpeople were voting for Reform, he
OL,10,Fsaid: "100%."
OL,12,F"Because my party and other parties
OL,13,Fhave let them down. We've got to a
OL,14,Fpoint where life has become
OL,15,Funaffordable and the status quo just
OL,16,Fhasn't delivered for them. And they're
OL,17,Fsending a message, aren't they? And
OL,18,Frightly in my view that, you know,
OL,19,Fthis just isn't good enough."
OL,26,@rD@GOUrD@MO]tD@AOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,F"It's time for politics to respond to
OL,7,Fthat message rather than promising
OL,8,Fbreakfast clubs or this, that and the
OL,9,Fother. No, I'm saying to you, Dan,
OL,10,Fwe've got to now hear what they're
OL,11,Fsaying."
OL,13,FFor Burnham, it seems time has come to
OL,14,F"take it on". The challenge of beating
OL,15,FReform ` and fixing his party.
OL,17,F"So, yeah, there's an element of risk.
OL,18,FBut, you know, I've taken the view
OL,19,Fthat the time has come for me to some
OL,20,Fways, you know, take it on and say,
OL,21,Fhere's what I think."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]vD@AOUvD@LO]yD@AOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,FUnlike former Green Party leader
OL,7,FCaroline Lucas, Burnham won't be
OL,8,Fcalling for other parties on the left
OL,9,Fof British politics ` the Greens or
OL,10,FLiberal Democrats ` to stand aside.
OL,12,F"I'm not going to sort of sit here
OL,13,Ftoday and pontificate about what other
OL,14,Fparties should do in this by election.
OL,15,FThat's honestly up for them" he told
OL,16,FITV News.
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779152631
OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,F"I will only just focus on what we
OL,7,Fneed to do. There's always an element
OL,8,Fof that. But the main thing is being
OL,9,Freally clear myself in what I am
OL,10,Fsaying and why I believe that
OL,11,Fhopefully should be worthy of people's
OL,12,Ftrust and support. So that's the
OL,13,Fapproach I'm bringing to this."
