OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,FBorrowing costs jumped to an 18 year
OL,7,Fhigh on Friday ` the same day that
OL,8,FLabour leadership speculation hit new
OL,9,Fhighs with rumors of a potential
OL,10,FBurnham challenge to Starmer.
OL,12,FOn Saturday, Burnham insisted his
OL,13,Feconomic plan was credible and that he
OL,14,Fwould stick to the current fiscal
OL,15,Frules.
OL,17,F"Number one, I have never said you can
OL,18,Fjust ignore the bond markets," he
OL,19,Finsisted.
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@^O]
