OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,F"I said that politicians have placed
OL,7,FBritain in hock because of the way in
OL,8,Fwhich we lost control of our finances
OL,9,Fand public spending. And that goes
OL,10,Fback to what I said to you before when
OL,11,Fwe, if you like handed away control of
OL,12,Fenergy, water, housing, that has left
OL,13,FBritain in a weak position when it
OL,14,Fcomes to public spending. You can't.
OL,16,F"How can you control public spending
OL,17,Fif you're chasing rents in the private
OL,18,Frented sector through the benefits
OL,19,Fsystem. How can that be done?
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
