OL,3,CAndy Burnham returns: I will take my
OL,4,Cfight 'as high as I can go'
OL,6,F"Let me say this really clearly. I
OL,7,Fsupport the fiscal rules. There needs
OL,8,Fto be a plan to get debt down, but
OL,9,Fbeyond that, we need to change
OL,10,Fpolitics and take the turbulence out
OL,11,Fof British politics because that is a
OL,12,Fcause of uncertainty that then has
OL,13,Fthat impact in the markets."
